The paper also involves the storage of a short bit vector, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.IT (Information Theory) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves analyzing bounds and improving them, which is a common theme in the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) sub-category. The paper also deals with the security of the scheme, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves analyzing the minimum number of bits of storage needed, which suggests that it may belong to the cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) sub-category.
